    "name": "几何射手",
    "steam_appid": 3136030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次射击都非常重要！你的目标是从移动的炮台发射炮弹，打向一片包含各种形状的几何体，每当你成功击中目标，这些几何体就会膨胀，变得更大，要完全打破它们需要多次精准射击，才能得分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136030/extras/b15e095a83fc449abeba9e7de459f84a.poster.avif?t=1732084788\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136030/extras/b15e095a83fc449abeba9e7de459f84a.webm?t=1732084788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136030/extras/b15e095a83fc449abeba9e7de459f84a.mp4?t=1732084788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时机和精准度是成功的关键！努力在一发子弹中打破多个形状，触发疯狂的连击，以获取最高分数。游戏的可爱艺术风格与富有挑战性的玩法相结合，可以小玩一会，也可以大战一场！还能挑战你的朋友，看看谁能获得最高分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136030/extras/074f9d4b33b9157fb10365b2ee4a206e.poster.avif?t=1732084788\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136030/extras/074f9d4b33b9157fb10365b2ee4a206e.webm?t=1732084788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136030/extras/074f9d4b33b9157fb10365b2ee4a206e.mp4?t=1732084788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情打个痛快，体验射击的乐趣吧！</p>",
